document_data.Notable Infernal Contracts:
* The agreement made by the [[arcanaloth]] [[Fetchtatter]] to the [[archdevil]] [[Bel]].
* The contract formed between High Overseer [[Thavius Kreeg]] and Archduke [[Zariel]] to save [[Elturel]] from destruction in [[1442 DR]].{{BG-DiA-time}}
* The debt accrued by [[Fai Chen]] to the [[rakshasa]] [[Mahadi]] of the [[Wandering Emporium]].{{Cite adventurers league/Faces of Fortune|7}}
* The agreement made between [[Krydle]] of [[Baldur's Gate]] and the [[erinyes]] [[Oreasha]] to save [[Shandie Freefoot]].<ref name='IT4-p1-4">{{Cite comic/Infernal Tides 4|1-4}}
